title.narrative: Second Community Agriculture Resource Management and Competitiveness Project

description.narrative: The Project Development Objective (PDO) is to (i) improve productivity and sustainability of pasture and livestock systems in targeted communities and (ii) increase the marketed production from selected livestock and high value agri-food value chains.
